&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:center">&lt;kbd>data-lyket-color-text&lt;/kbd>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:center">버튼 텍스트 색상 지정&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:center">&lt;kbd>data-lyket-color-highlight&lt;/kbd>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:center">사용자가 버튼 클릭 시 애니메이션 색상&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table></description></item><item><title>[Template] 템플릿</title><link>https://leenago-dev.github.io/p/template-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://leenago-dev.github.io/p/template-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://leenago-dev.github.io/p/template-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF/about.jpg" alt="Featured image of post [Template] 템플릿" />&lt;p>This article offers a sample of basic Markdown syntax that can be used in Hugo content files, also it shows whether basic HTML elements are decorated with CSS in a Hugo theme.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>참고)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash; 북마크 &amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&amp;mdash;&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>이렇게 밑줄도 그을 수 있군요&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="headings">&lt;a href="#headings" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>Headings
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>목차 Numbering은 &lt;code>##(H2)&lt;/code>부터 시작이 됩니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code># (H1)&lt;/code>부터 &lt;code>###### (H6)&lt;/code>까지 있습니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="paragraph">&lt;a href="#paragraph" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>Paragraph
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>단락 설정은 &lt;mark>Enter&lt;/mark> 로 설정할 수 있습니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>글을 이렇게 작성하다가&amp;hellip;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Enter 두 번으로 완성!&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="blockquotes--quote-shortcode">&lt;a href="#blockquotes--quote-shortcode" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>Blockquotes &amp;amp; Quote Shortcode
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>인용구 삽입 방법입니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>아래 &lt;strong>Quote Shortcode&lt;/strong>와 같이 알아보겠습니다.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="blockquotes">&lt;a href="#blockquotes" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>Blockquotes
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="blockquote-without-attribution">&lt;a href="#blockquote-without-attribution" class="header-anchor">&lt;/a>Blockquote without attribution
&lt;/h4>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Tiam, ad mint andaepu dandae nostion secatur sequo quae.
&lt;strong>Note&lt;/strong> that you can use &lt;em>Markdown syntax&lt;/em> within a blockquote.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
